  "description": "Remove Top Spacing from Embedded Gallery Item in Single Post View\n\nEliminate the unwanted blank space appearing above images in embedded-gallery-item cards when viewing individual posts.\n\nRequirements:\n- Locate the embedded-gallery-item component used in single post view\n- Identify the CSS property or element causing the top spacing (padding, margin, or structural element)\n- Remove or adjust the spacing so the image aligns flush with the top of the card\n- Ensure the fix applies only to single post view and doesn't affect gallery items in other contexts\n- Verify the change doesn't break image aspect ratios or cause layout shifts\n- Test with multiple image sizes and aspect ratios to ensure consistent behavior",
